Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:51.88,EDJVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必死に答えを探す　バカみたいだね  あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.08,0:23:56.77,EDJVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}目と目を合わせたら　怖がらずに　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:24:01.15,EDJVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}話してみよう　自分だけの心を
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:08.28,EDJVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ため息をついて　さぁ　リセットしよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:49.06,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4\1a&HA0&\3a&HBE&\4a&HDB&}贴近内心  用自己的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:51.86,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4\1a&HA0&\3a&HBE&\4a&HDB&}大胆说出真正的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:06.71,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4\1a&HA0&\3a&HBE&\4a&HDB&\t(2300,2700,\1a&H00&\3a&H50&\4a&HC8&)}平凡的星期五  沮丧的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:10.48,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}充满无尽的不安和悔意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:16.84,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}每天不停思考  用尽全部时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:20.02,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}这份心意该如何表达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:26.46,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}每当你的眼神飘忽不定  我的心便满是不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:31.64,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}不想被你发觉  脑海中却一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:36.55,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}其实我  只希望  能永远和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:41.62,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}这是我纯情的告白  请你认真对待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:46.66,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}或许我  还依然  无法轻易将你放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:51.88,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}拼命寻找答案的我  实在太不聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.08,0:23:56.77,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}当视线相遇之时  请不要感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:24:01.15,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}向我坦诚你心底的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:08.28,EDCVertical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp-4}轻轻叹一口气  再重新出发
